data.text: FH Joanneum is one of the largest Universities of Applied Sciences in Austria. It has about 3,500 students and about 530 employees (figures from 2009/10 academic year). The main campus is located in Graz, while there are two other locations in Kapfenberg and Bad Gleichenberg.
